      • getWeight

        public Weight getWeight()
        Description copied from interface: GroundCompatibilityKernel
        Returns the Weight of this GroundCompatibilityKernel.

        Until GroundCompatibilityKernel.setWeight(Weight) is called, this GroundKernel's weight is the current weight of its parent Kernel. After it is called, it remains the most recent Weight set by GroundCompatibilityKernel.setWeight(Weight).
